products.name: Tool Bag - Sand
products.description: Also made from our waxed canvass collection, the Fren Tool Bag fits all your everyday essentials. Its structure has a round base and has four (4) outer pockets for other essentials and a handle-sling combination. One additional feature is a small secret pocket on the inside of one of the handles for bills or any small item.

products.name: Tour Tote - Bone
products.description: The Tour Tote is a large sack designed to fit just about anything, a yoga mat included! It is made of waxed canvas and, like fine wine, improves over time. With its marks and creases eventually creating a rich patina, it makes for a unique personal piece as it ages.
